 I bought this TV to replace a smaller 20 year old Sony. It is used in the kitchen.
Nice picture (coming from a 720p resolution 20 year old Sony). Nice feature set in terms of being 'smart'. I was able to modify an adjustable height monitor stand that I already had so I could mount the new set. As you can see, my kitchen cabinets limited my overall height. I was able to mount the new sound bar underneath the tv and made a nice compact package. Make sure you buy a set with the inputs and outputs you need. There are many choices and the more features there are, the higher the price. This was fine for what I needed.


